description:
This tiny miniature house is carved from a single piece of XPS-foam. In this short D&D terrain tutorial I wanted to see if it is possible to save lots of time by crafting everything from one piece. Larger, high-effort houses will be carved in the future! Subscribe!: https://tinyurl.com/y2qxwefo
